Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Media coverage of looting
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407j1l
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 7 Aug 1977
Suggestion that radio coverage during NY blackout fuelled outbreaks of looting. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.